Package: scCloneVar
Type: Package
Title: Clonal Variance and Heterogeneity Analysis for Single-Cell Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Xunxuan", "Chen", 
           email = "xunxuanc@usc.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    scCloneVar provides tools for clonal tracing analysis in single-cell 
    transcriptomics data, including output activity scoring, clone-wise 
    differential expression, variance modeling, PCA-based heterogeneity 
    quantification, and MSigDB-based enrichment analysis.
